	<section>
	<title>AlternativeFriendlyFormatFromNow(System.DateTime date) 
: System.String
</title>

<p>
 Alternative representation of a difference between the specified date and now. If within 24hr it returns <tt>Today</tt>. If within 48hr it returns <tt>Yesterday</tt>. If within 40 days it returns <tt>x days ago</tt> and otherwise it returns <tt>x months ago</tt><p> TODO: Think about i18n </p>
</p>



	<p>
	<table class="commontable">
	<tr>
		<th>Parameter</th>
		<th>Description</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><tt>date</tt></td>
		<td>
The date in the past (should be equal or less than now)
		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
	</p>
	</section>
